data.text: GO FIRST salutes the quick actions of its crew. Via a video conference call, Mr. Kaushik Khona - CEO & other senior members of GO FIRST joined the passenger & the doctor in a felicitation ceremony to present mementos to the crew.

Working together as a team, the doctor & a crew member performed CPR and used the AED to help the passenger recover from this life-threatening emergency. It was indeed a flight of angels - the crew & doctor that saved the life of the passenger!

Our crew members #Abhishek , #Shilpa , #Sumeet & #Imlitemsula were quick to respond & rushed to the aid of the passenger. From the rigorous training that the crew receive, they were quick to calm fellow passengers & identify a doctor on board. https://t.co/R9BGEkqSZ9
